              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The Beam was Degraded from Its Nominal Extraction",
                "Energy of 102 MeV by Passing Through Beryllium Foils.",
                "Range-Energy Values were Taken from C.F.Williamson+,",
                "Cea-R3042(1966). Targets Consisted of a Stack of",
                "Three Al-Foils, the Centre One Being Used in the",
                "Analysis, the Outer Ones Serving As Guard Foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Aluminium Foil, Enrichment 99.99%, Thickness 19.8",
                "Micrometer."
              ]
            }
          ],
