              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The Experimental Results are Compared to Calculations",
                "In the Framework of the Exciton Model. A Possible",
                "Contribution of a He-3 Producing Reaction Mechanism",
                "Is Discussed."
              ]
            }
          ],
